            <title>YUNZII“木坨坨”三模机械键盘 WOOD 68 / 84 国行发售，449 元起</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/966/729.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/966/729.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Sun, 21 Jun 2026 13:45:14 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 6 月 21 日消息，YUNZII（键设宇宙）今年 4 月的时候宣布了外壳采用胡桃木材质的三模机械键盘 WOOD 68 和 WOOD 84。现在这两款产品也已在国行发售，<strong>定价 449 元 / 479 元</strong>。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="342" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/4/802923b3-e44a-435a-9169-3740efd9964b.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="YUNZII“木坨坨”三模机械键盘 WOOD 68 / 84 国行发售，449 元起" width="1440" /></p><p>WOOD 68 / 84 均支持三模连接，配备 130hr 续航 4000mAh 电池；内部采用 Tray Mount 船壳结构，PCB 支持热插拔并具备南向 ARGB 背光，拥有 5 层吸声填充。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="461" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/4/8a12655a-47e6-4d72-8cef-522cafe2147d.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="YUNZII“木坨坨”三模机械键盘 WOOD 68 / 84 国行发售，449 元起" width="1440" /></p><p>其搭载 YUNZII 糖果轴，拥有线性手感，触发力 45±5gf、触底力 51±5gf，触发行程 2.0±0.4mm、触底行程 3.3±0.4mm.；配套原厂 (CHERRY) 高度 PBT 材质二色注塑工艺键帽。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="773" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/6/0846a3cd-1c74-420f-8abd-84bad4626037.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="YUNZII“木坨坨”三模机械键盘 WOOD 68 / 84 国行发售，449 元起" width="790" /></p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://uland.taobao.com/coupon/edetail?e=qOOASM3UV3%2BlhHvvyUNXZfh8CuWt5YH5OVuOuRD5gLJMmdsrkidbOUV9IBA4kmjL1HKhzLgZ9V7LNfvwUpvZU9%2Fd1l5yRB4LJpW8EhlDmp9WpatAKnIYP9uvFBno3tjhv28yw4ElEIdyBOK%2B8KjzSsa1jpueNohd4pjtu38nF6IrpfoV5flOUh%2BW5Vb9gCLx%2BMUwzxYlSKFDy9dwU5aH9VGFPIwCkrMVRV6p%2BYfKYJaZNVnwn%2BFJVijdfAKMf4s7JSDAi30qQ2pF6B2qje0XtWECTcnADCY9l8SlxnzaPt2%2FzOVvQe539ULDruQHxnOEhAlwBqUZweRlBRYM90QVRw%3D%3D&amp;traceId=213e047817820495772896299e0c63&amp;&amp;union_lens=lensId:TAPI@1782049577@0b56803f_149d_19eea6e998c_315c@01" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img.alicdn.com/bao/uploaded/i4/2215000700668/O1CN01KnQu0W1Gnzif50Rbf_!!4611686018427385596-0-item_pic.jpg" title="YUNZII“木坨坨”三模机械键盘 WOOD 68 / 84 国行发售，449 元起" 